      "description": "Looking for a cheap set of wheels with plenty of life left for the right buyer? This one isn\u2019t perfect, but it\u2019s an honest car that could make a great budget commuter, first project, or handy spare to have around. It\u2019s priced to reflect the wear, and for someone practical who doesn\u2019t mind a bit of TLC, there\u2019s real value here. If you want something affordable and straightforward without spending a fortune, this could be a smart buy.",
